      <!-- よくある質問 -->
      <section class="qa">
       
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="bg-letter"> <div class="bg_font">FAQ</div></div>    
          <h2 class="title">よくある質問</h2>
          </div>
           <div class="wrap2">
            <ul>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa1">
              <label for="qa1">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">初期費用、月額費用はいくらでしょうか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
                
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">月間の受注件数やご利用規模によって最適なプランが異なります。事業規模に合わせて無理のない予算でお使いいただけるプラン設計になっておりますので、お気軽にお問い合せください。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa2">
              <label for="qa2">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">最低契約期間はありますか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
                
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">期限は設けておりません。いつでも解約いただけます。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa3">
              <label for="qa3">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">LP一体型フォームを使いたいのですが、どのプランから使えるのでしょうか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
                
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">すべてのプランで無料で無制限でご利用いただけます。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa4">
              <label for="qa4">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">他社カートシステムや基幹システムからの移行は可能でしょうか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
               
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">可能です。移行作業についても詳細にご案内いたしますのでお気軽にお問い合わせください。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa5">
              <label for="qa5">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">初めてのEC事業の立ち上げなのですが知見がないので不安です。相談することは可能でしょうか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
               
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">可能です。月商3億円越えのEC運営経験者をはじめ、100社以上のEC事業立ち上げを支援してきた元プロジェクトマネージャなど業界知識の豊富なリピストアカウンティングチームがサポートいたします</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa6">
              <label for="qa6">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">デザインのカスタマイズは可能ですか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
               
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">すべてのページを独自にカスタマイズすることが可能です。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" id="qa7">
              <label for="qa7">
                <svg class="q-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="21" viewBox="0 0 18 21" fill="none">
                  <path d="M16.2275 16.3195L17.8115 18.2115C16.7995 19.4435 15.3475 20.1035 13.6535 20.1035C11.3655 20.1035 9.75945 19.2675 7.38345 16.7595C3.15945 16.2315 0.189453 13.0415 0.189453 8.86146C0.189453 4.28546 3.75345 0.897461 8.61545 0.897461C13.4555 0.897461 17.0415 4.26346 17.0415 8.86146C17.0415 12.4695 14.8195 15.3295 11.5415 16.3855C12.2895 17.1775 12.9495 17.4635 13.7195 17.4635C14.6655 17.4635 15.5015 17.0895 16.2275 16.3195ZM3.79745 8.86146C3.79745 11.7875 5.86545 13.7895 8.61545 13.7895C11.3655 13.7895 13.4335 11.7875 13.4335 8.86146C13.4335 5.93546 11.3655 3.93346 8.61545 3.93346C5.86545 3.93346 3.79745 5.93546 3.79745 8.86146Z"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="text">広告タグや計測タグなど各種タグの設置は可能ですか？</div>
                <div class="btn-outer">
                  <svg class="btn-open" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none">
                    <rect y="5.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                    <rect x="5.5" y="13" width="13" height="2" transform="rotate(-90 5.5 13)" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  <svg class="btn-close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="3" viewBox="0 0 13 3" fill="none">
                    <rect y="0.5" width="13" height="2" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </label>
              <div class="answer">
                <div class="content">
                  <svg class="a-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="17" viewBox="0 0 18 17" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13.8952 16.1998L12.5312 12.8998H5.38123L4.01723 16.1998H0.365234L7.22923 0.799805H10.7492L17.6352 16.1998H13.8952ZM6.52524 10.1938H11.4092L8.96723 4.29781L6.52524 10.1938Z" fill="#28A108"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="text">可能です。管理画面上で一元管理するタグマネージャー機能がございます。Google Tag ManagerやGoogle Analyticsなども設置可能です。</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
       <!-- CTA3 -->
